\begin_layout Standard
Another good example of 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

freezing point lowering
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is in the manufacture of Portland cement by the process of 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

klinkering.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 There are two compounds produced by this process, 
\begin_inset Formula $(CaO)_{2}SiO_{2}$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
