\end_inset


\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

cement speak
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $(CaO)_{3}SiO_{2}$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $C_{3}S$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 These compounds, when pulverized to powders and mixed with water, react
 to form the so-called C-S-H gel (
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

H
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{2}O$
\end_inset

 or OH), the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

glue
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 that upon 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

hardening
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 holds everything together in mortar (Portland cement plus sand) and concrete
