\end_inset

 range.
 Since this is now at least a ternary system (
\begin_inset Formula $CaO$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $SiO_{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $Al_{2}O_{3}$
\end_inset

), we will come back to the phase diagram when considering Type III phase
