\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

kills
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

) the length of football fields, 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{2}S$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{3}S$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

balls
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 (referred to by the German word, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

klinker
