\end_inset

) tumble in their quasi-equilibrium liquid.
 Imagine an overall composition midway between 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

A
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $C_{2}S/C_{3}S$
\end_inset

) and the eutectic composition in Fig.
 
