 Only at the left and right extremes of the phase diagram do we have 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

 solid solution by itself (
\begin_inset Formula $X_{A}\rightarrow1$
\end_inset

) or 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

 solid solution by itself (
\begin_inset Formula $X_{B}\rightarrow1$
\end_inset

).
