\begin_layout Standard
The lattice parameter of 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma-Fe$
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $a_{o}$
\end_inset

) is known to be 0.37 nm, such that the face-diagonal is 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{2}a_{o}$
\end_inset

.
 The jump distance shown is half of that distance, or 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{2}a_{o}/2$
\end_inset

, which would be 0.26 nm.
